					  FINAL RESULTS: 2011 ADGA Golfer of the Year  

					 by Allen Freeman  |  October 2, 2011    No Comments  

					 

  Jim Krivanek gets the GOY trophy from Dave Chapple, while Tim Davis presents to Senior Jim Cea  
 FINAL RESULTS: AKRON DISTRICT GOLF ASSN 
2011 GOLFER OF THE YEAR TOURNAMENT 
RD1: Firestone Country Club West Course – Par 70 
RD2: Firestone Country Club North Course – Par 72 
RD3: Firestone Country Club South Course – Par 70 
